	(text "GPIO2	Input to detect rising edge \n		of the Debug Mode switch to \n		exit sleep mode.\nGPIO4	Input to monitor the Activate \n		the OLED display.\nGPIO7	Input to monitor the state \n		of the Debug Mode switch.\nGPIO36	Output, to active the 3v used\n		to power the 1-wire."
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 144.018 27.94 0)
